_sText:
A bomb/defuse map set inside a nightclub. Terrorist try to bomb either the arcade snack room or the office above the arcade.
============================================================================================================================
Setting was too dark so I lit it up a little.
2 cameras, 1 in the office above arcade that views dance floor. The other in the DJ booth that views the office (one of the bombing sites). The DJ booth also has 3 switches, 1 for music, 1 for smoke and 1 for some cool light effects on the floor.
